24:22.700 --> 24:24.000
MORE ABOUT YOU.

24:24.800 --> 24:26.600
RENEE...

24:27.200 --> 24:29.000
IT'S JUST A LITTLE
TOO WEIRD.

24:29.000 --> 24:30.700
COME ON.

24:31.600 --> 24:34.800
